# Enterprise Portal AI-Native Engineering Operating Model

## Vision

Transform the existing enterprise portal from a functional prototype into an AI-assisted, specification-driven engineering platform.

The objective is not simply to improve the current implementation, but to establish a sustainable engineering operating model where every enhancement follows a governed lifecycle driven by domain specifications, architectural decisions, security by design, automated testing, and AI-assisted development.

The portal should become the reference implementation for AI-native enterprise software engineering.

---

# Current State

## Existing Strengths

* Functional baseline implementation
* Domain-Driven Design (DDD)
* Specification-Driven Development (SDD)
* Domain-based functional specifications
* Clear frontend/backend separation
* Existing architecture documentation

## Engineering Gaps

* Limited automated regression testing
* Inconsistent engineering practices
* AI used primarily for implementation rather than engineering
* Security reviews occur too late
* Product decisions are not consistently traceable
* Architectural decisions are not formally captured
* No standardized engineering workflow

---

# Engineering Principles

1. Business domains own functionality.
2. Specifications are the source of truth.
3. Architecture evolves intentionally through documented decisions.
4. Security is designed in, not added later.
5. Product decisions precede technical decisions.
6. Tests protect every architectural change.
7. AI augments engineering discipline rather than replacing it.
8. Every implementation must be traceable to a specification.
9. Every decision should be reviewable and reproducible.

---

# Engineering Decision Flow

Every feature must progress through the following engineering decision flow.

```text
Business Need
        │
        ▼
Product Persona
        │
        ▼
Domain Specification
        │
        ▼
Security Persona
        │
        ▼
Threat Assessment
        │
        ▼
Architecture Persona
        │
        ▼
Technical Design
        │
        ▼
Engineering Persona
        │
        ▼
Task Breakdown
        │
        ▼
QA Persona
        │
        ▼
Test Design (TDD)
        │
        ▼
Implementation
        │
        ▼
AI Review
        │
        ▼
Human Review
        │
        ▼
CI/CD
        │
        ▼
Deployment
```

No implementation begins until the engineering decision flow has completed.

