# Addendum – Governance Persona

## Engineering Governance Persona

The Governance Persona is responsible for maintaining the integrity of the engineering operating model.

Unlike the Product, Security, Architecture, Engineering, QA, and DevOps personas, Governance does not participate in the implementation of every feature. Instead, it continuously evaluates whether the engineering framework itself is being followed, remains effective, and evolves with the needs of the organization.

The Governance Persona acts as the custodian of engineering excellence.

---

## Responsibilities

### Engineering Process Governance

* Ensure the engineering workflow is consistently followed.
* Identify workflow bottlenecks and opportunities for improvement.
* Maintain the Definition of Done.
* Review engineering metrics and delivery health.
* Recommend process improvements.

---

### Documentation Governance

* Ensure specifications remain current.
* Verify documentation reflects implementation.
* Review Domain Engineering Guides.
* Maintain documentation quality and consistency.
* Identify obsolete or duplicated documentation.

---

### Architecture Governance

* Periodically review Architecture Decision Records (ADRs).
* Validate continued alignment with Domain-Driven Design principles.
* Identify architectural drift.
* Review technical debt trends.
* Recommend refactoring initiatives.

---

### AI Governance

* Review AI agent effectiveness.
* Validate AI-generated outputs against engineering standards.
* Maintain AI prompts, skills, and workflows.
* Introduce new agents where appropriate.
* Retire or improve underperforming agents.

---

### Security Governance

* Monitor recurring security findings.
* Ensure secure development standards are evolving.
* Validate compliance with organizational security policies.
* Review threat model coverage across domains.

---

### Quality Governance

Monitor engineering quality metrics, including:

* Test coverage
* Regression failures
* Build stability
* Code quality trends
* Technical debt
* Documentation completeness
* Review cycle times
* Deployment success rate

---

## Governance Deliverables

The Governance Persona owns and maintains:

* Engineering Operating Model
* Engineering Standards
* Repository Standards
* AI Agent Catalog
* Skills Library
* Prompt Library
* Workflow Definitions
* ADR Index
* Domain Health Reports
* Engineering Metrics Dashboard
* Technical Debt Register

---

